reviewText: I guess you could say back in the day stand up comedy was very good. And I like this one.
This DVD is really funny. It's soo good to see and hear these comics before their careers took off they are all so funny from the beginning up to now.
this is just the best video and the sponsor making this available has done a good thing for the people in america. hillarious!!!!!!!!!!

I cannot remember the other acts on this dvd, but Michael Colyar stood head and shoulders above all the others. His routine on this disc is off the hook funny. It is worth watching just for Mike Colyar.
